title: 4 Weeks Free!  Lakeshore District - 2 Bedroom Apartment
posting_body: ['4 weeks free!', 'This special is NOT included in the price listed.', 'Brand new complex located just off East Riverside.', 'Be the first to live in this unit.', 'Currently the cheapest new option within a 15 minute proximity to downtown and Lady Bird Lake.', 'In your brand new unit enjoy:', '- Hardfloors throughout and carpet in bedroom', '- Chrome fixtures', '- LED Lighting', '- Quartz Countertops', 'Enjoy community amenities such as:', '- Expansive two story gym', '- Dog Park', '- Lounge and gaming space', '- Lawn areas', '- Working areas', '- Sparkling Pool', '- Trail Access', 'I am a Realtor/apartment locator in the Austin area.', 'My services are 100% free, don’t hesitate to give me a call.', " If you'd like to learn more about this property, or would like to review other available options, call/text or email me.", 'Also at Grackle Realty, if looking to buy, we focus on educating renters on how to become home owners.', 'Follow us on our Instagram to learn more!', 'Jacob Hannusch', 'Grackle Realty', 'show contact info', '*I strive to keep my postings up to date, but pricing and availability are both subject to change.*']
